#Text=NOTfCE —The “• Chief Justice ” Lodge of ANTEDILUVIAN BUFFALOES is removed to the above house, and the meetings held as usual.
#Text=A BAZAAR in aid of the FORESTERS’ FRIENDLY SOCIETY will be opened on the 26th day of December, 1866, in the Assembly Room of the Mechanics’ Institute, Stalybridge.

#Text=The above is intended to lesson the debt existing upon the Foresters’, and to provide means of shelter for the poor and infirm Members of the Order, as well as to educate the Orphan’s of deceased Members.
#Text=The friends of charity will please forward contributions of money, or articles of clothing for sale, or otherwise, to the following persons :—Mr.
#Text=HOPWOOD, Portland Place ; or any of the Committee.
#Text=The Circulation of the IREPORTER exceeds Eight Thousand Copies weekly, and is rapidly increasing.
#Text=IVe this day issue Eight Thousand Three Hundred Copies of our earliest edition.
